Scope Description <code>gmail.send</code> Send emails only <code>gmail.readonly</code> Read emails only <code>gmail.modify</code> Read, send, delete emails <code>gmail.labels</code> Manage labels <pre><code>import "github.com/grokify/gogoogle/gmailutil/v1"

scopes := []string{gmailutil.GmailSendScope}
</code></pre>

Scope Constant Description Send only <code>GmailSendScope</code> Send emails Read only <code>GmailReadonlyScope</code> Read emails Modify <code>GmailModifyScope</code> Read, send, delete Full access <code>GmailScope</code> All operations <pre><code>import "github.com/grokify/gogoogle/gmailutil/v1"

// For sending only
scopes := []string{gmailutil.GmailSendScope}

// For full access
scopes := []string{gmailutil.GmailScope}
</code></pre>

Scope Description <code>spreadsheets.readonly</code> Read spreadsheets <code>spreadsheets</code> Read and write spreadsheets <pre><code>scopes := []string{
    "https://www.googleapis.com/auth/spreadsheets.readonly",
}
</code></pre>
